posts.post_title: WTB ~ Raw or Low Grade Gandil(s)
posts.post_content: Looking for raw (not trimmed) or lower graded examples of ol’ Chick in any back. Can do $$ or possibly work out a trade.
Dang…… got excited for a sec when “Bobbleywrights” PM’d me letting me know that his little brother has a bunch of “Gandels” that he’ll sell me for a good price if I “kindly text him on his gmail”. 😁
